DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
7729::$$$message_0075_0000_0000$$$::Unlike Shinto, there is no sign of people anywhere in Miyama.[lr]::
7730::$$$message_0075_0000_0001$$$::There is nobody around after eight at night, and the town is silent and still.::
7731::$$$message_0075_0001_0000$$$::The house I saw this morning stands across the intersection.[lr]::
7732::$$$message_0075_0001_0001$$$::There are no signs of life, and a "No Trespassing" sign hangs over the front door.::
7733::$$$message_0075_0002_0000$$$::In just a single day, the house has fallen quiet, almost like an abandoned building.[lr]::
7734::$$$message_0075_0002_0001$$$::A girl and her parents were killed by a burglar.[lr]::
7735::$$$message_0075_0002_0002$$$::I wonder what life awaits now for the single child who survived.::
7736::$$$message_0075_0003_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
7737::$$$message_0075_0003_0001$$$::I bite my lip, frustrated by my powerlessness.[lr]::
7738::$$$message_0075_0003_0002$$$::I promised I'd be just like Kiritsugu, but I couldn't do anything, even when something like this happens so close to home.[lr]::
7739::$$$message_0075_0003_0003$$$::I want to help people, but I don't even know what I CAN do.::
7740::$$$message_0075_0004_0000$$$::I reach the top of the hill where my house sits.[lr]::
7741::$$$message_0075_0004_0001$$$::The lights are on, so Fuji-nee or Sakura are still inside.::
7742::$$$message_0075_0005_0000$$$::"I'm home... Oh, it's just you, Fuji-nee."[lr]::
7743::$$$message_0075_0005_0001$$$::"Hm? Oh, welcome back, Shirou."[lr]::
7744::$$$message_0075_0005_0002$$$::Fuji-nee turns toward me, munching on a rice cracker.[lr]::
7745::$$$message_0075_0005_0003$$$::The TV is tuned to a lively variety show.::
7746::$$$message_0075_0006_0000$$$::"You're home late again. Didn't I tell you to come home earlier since it gets dark so fast in winter?"[lr]::
7747::$$$message_0075_0006_0001$$$::"I AM home early. I had work until eight, so get off my back about that.[lr]::
7748::$$$message_0075_0006_0002$$$::So where's Sakura? I see dinner's already prepared."::
7749::$$$message_0075_0007_0000$$$::"Sakura went home early. She said she had something to do today, so she just came and made dinner."[lr]::
7750::$$$message_0075_0007_0001$$$::Fuji-nee cheerfully replies.[lr]::
7751::$$$message_0075_0007_0002$$$::As far as she's concerned, anyone who makes her food is a good person.::
7752::$$$message_0075_0008_0000$$$::"I see. That's probably a good thing for now. It's been dangerous lately, so maybe I'll take over making dinner until the new school term starts."[lr]::
7753::$$$message_0075_0008_0001$$$::"Uh...objection! You come home so late, if you make dinner when you get back, I won't get to eat until after ten!"::
7754::$$$message_0075_0009_0000$$$::"Um, couldn't you just eat at home?"[lr]::
7755::$$$message_0075_0009_0001$$$::"What are you talking about? This is my home."[lr]::
7756::$$$message_0075_0009_0002$$$::Fuji-nee tilts her head, puzzled.[lr]::
7757::$$$message_0075_0009_0003$$$::Honestly, I'm not sure if a response like that should make me happy or sad.::
7758::$$$message_0075_0010_0000$$$::"Sheesh, fine. I know it's pointless asking you to make dinner.[lr]::
7759::$$$message_0075_0010_0001$$$::By the way, what's that you've got there? You didn't bring over more junk, did you?" ::
7760::$$$message_0075_0011_0000$$$::Fuji-nee has a tendency to leave a bunch of junk here.[lr]::
7761::$$$message_0075_0011_0001$$$::She'll bring stuff like bowls from restaurants that are too big to be functional, an unnecessarily heavy earthen teapot, or a weird guitar that plays itself. She must think this place is convenient storage or something.::
7762::$$$message_0075_0012_0000$$$::"Show it to me. I'm going to toss it if it's trash."[lr]::
7763::$$$message_0075_0012_0001$$$::"This thing? It's just a poster."[lr]::
7764::$$$message_0075_0012_0002$$$::Fuji-nee hands me the poster.[lr]::
7765::$$$message_0075_0012_0003$$$::It's probably a poster of some no-name singer.::
7766::$$$message_0075_0013_0000$$$::"Let's see..."[lr]::
7767::$$$message_0075_0013_0001$$$::I knew it. It's a poster of a young man wearing a military uniform smiling with his thumbs up, all in front of a cheap-looking blue sky background.[lr]::
7768::$$$message_0075_0013_0002$$$::The caption on the poster, in bloody font: [lr]::
7769::$$$message_0075_0013_0003$$$::                                  "Love's Lovely Ranger Land.[lr]::
7770::$$$message_0075_0013_0004$$$::                                  Come to the Self-Defense Meet-Up"[r]::
7771::$$$message_0075_0013_0005$$$::Hey, this is a recruitment poster for a youth group!::
7772::$$$message_0075_0014_0000$$$::"I don't want it, so you can have it."[lr]::
7773::$$$message_0075_0014_0001$$$::"I don't want this either!"[lr]::
7774::$$$message_0075_0014_0002$$$::I quickly roll the poster back up and try to whack Fuji-nee on the head with it.::
7775::$$$message_0075_0015_0000$$$::"Heh heh. You missed!"[lr]::
7776::$$$message_0075_0015_0001$$$::However...[lr]::
7777::$$$message_0075_0015_0002$$$::Fuji-nee counters mercilessly with another poster she'd been holding.[lr]::
7778::$$$message_0075_0015_0003$$$::Konk.[lr]::
7779::$$$message_0075_0015_0004$$$::Her poster-sword bops me lightl[line2]::
7780::$$$message_0075_0016_0000$$$::"Gah!"[lr]::
7781::$$$message_0075_0016_0001$$$::Stars! I see stars!::
7782::$$$message_0075_0017_0000$$$::"Heh heh heh. You thought you were going to hit me? You'll need to up your game, if you ever hope to do that."[lr]::
7783::$$$message_0075_0017_0001$$$::"Ugh. Th-that's not the issue here! How the hell does a paper poster make a sound like that!?"[lr]::
7784::$$$message_0075_0017_0002$$$::Did she manage some sort of technique only a true poster master can execute!?::
7785::$$$message_0075_0018_0000$$$::"Eh? Oh sorry, sorry. My poster's a collector's edition, made of fancy plate steel.[lr]::
7786::$$$message_0075_0018_0001$$$::Is your head okay, Shirou?"[lr]::
7787::$$$message_0075_0018_0002$$$::"...Fuji-nee. You're going to end up killing someone one of these days."::
7788::$$$message_0075_0019_0000$$$::"Eh heh heh. If that time ever comes, it'll all be good because you'll sweep in and marry me!"[lr]::
7789::$$$message_0075_0019_0001$$$::"Yeah. Not a chance. I'm not marrying a natural born killer."::
7790::$$$message_0075_0020_0000$$$::"What? I don't think I'm that violent."[lr]::
7791::$$$message_0075_0020_0001$$$::"You [font italic=true]would[font italic=false] be that unaware of your actions."[lr]::
7792::$$$message_0075_0020_0002$$$::Pray that I survive.[lr]::
7793::$$$message_0075_0020_0003$$$::I'll have to be very careful from now on if I am going to have any hope of avoiding being murdered.::
7794::$$$message_0075_0021_0000$$$::"Keep talking big. But now I'm hungry, Shirou. I've been waiting for so long, so let's hurry and EAT already."[lr]::
7795::$$$message_0075_0021_0001$$$::Fuji-nee gets up.[lr]::
7796::$$$message_0075_0021_0002$$$::What's up with Fuji-nee? She must be really hungry if she's offering to help...even if it's just help setting the table.::
7797::$$$message_0075_0022_0000$$$::"Fine. Then you take out the plates and bowls. You can at least scoop the rice into bowls, right?"[lr]::
7798::$$$message_0075_0022_0001$$$::"Of course I can. Hey, do you think it'll be okay if I use a bigger rice bowl?"[lr]::
7799::$$$message_0075_0022_0002$$$::"That shouldn't be a problem. Sakura's not here today, so we'll definitely have leftovers."[lr]::
7800::$$$message_0075_0022_0003$$$::"Good, good. Then you and I will have matching bowls today."[lr]::
7801::$$$message_0075_0022_0004$$$::Fuji-nee scoops mounds of rice into the two large bowls.::
7802::$$$message_0075_0023_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
7803::$$$message_0075_0023_0001$$$::Whatever. I was going to go for a second helping anyway, and if I meddle in what Fuji-nee does now, we may really not have any dinner.[lr]::
7804::$$$message_0075_0023_0002$$$::Besides...[lr]::
7805::$$$message_0075_0023_0003$$$::This is the kind of chaotic scene dinner at my home has been for years.::
7806::$$$message_0075_0024_0000$$$::Another day ends.[lr]::
7807::$$$message_0075_0024_0001$$$::We finish our rowdy dinner, and after I see off Fuji-nee, I take a bath.[lr]::
7808::$$$message_0075_0024_0002$$$::After that, I head to the shed for my daily training.[lr]::
7809::$$$message_0075_0024_0003$$$::I complete it as usual, and then go to sleep.[lr]::
7810::$$$message_0075_0024_0004$$$::It's one o'clock in the morning.[lr]::
7811::$$$message_0075_0024_0005$$$::Today ends peacefully and without incident.:Ą9Æ